ActJobs and Growth Act, 2012
SubjectOrder Fixing March 7, 2013 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing March 7, 2013, as the day on which subsections 433(1) and (3), 434(1), 435(1), (2), (4), (6) and (8), 436(1), (4), (5) and (7), 437(1), (3) and (5), 438(1), 439(1), 440(1) and (3), 441(1), 442(1), 443(1) and 445(2), sections 447 and 452 to 460 and subsection 461(1) of the JOBS AND GROWTH ACT, 2012, chapter 31 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE.
